caption.text:
High School, at first maybe worst place of all, where we all hoped to get out of here real fast. But, in the end, we all realized that this is the best place ever.

Where sweet, sour, and bitter memories we cherished until our last breath. Where we meet siblings from another blood whom we love for now and for times to come.
Where some of us find the part of their hearts, part of their life, and become together until Hades comes apart.

A place full of the most precious on earth. That upon having it, you will condemn a diamond as worthless compared to it. That upon being with it, a raging storm passes by just like a breezing wind. It is a family. Not by flesh and blood, but, by the every moment we walked in.

High school may not be easy, it never was. But, it's totally WORTH IT.

Now the time has come. A Midsummer Night Dream must come to an end. As the Dawn of Reality announces a new day...a new beginning. 
The sparkling stars and the beautiful lunar from the night may have faded, but that doesn't mean they're gone or you lost them. It's just mean that you can't see them as the dazzling sun arose, but they are still there. 
We are all stars and moon to each other. All of us exploring the universe together, rotating around the sun called 'life', we may not see each other as much as before, because the rensponsibility of life. Then another night will come, with different stars from tonight, maybe they will be our next family. But don't lose heart, don't forget about this family, cause there will be another starry night when you can see the same stars and moon as tonight again and thus, reunited with this family again.

In the end, we may not standing under the same school rooftop, but we are still standing under the same one Sky. We may not standing on the same school floor, but we are still standing on the same one Earth. 
A sincerest thank you, from the bottom of my heart XKoteka, Sepatwo, D'LastSex, Teachers, and all of you Hwa Ind 2012-2015üòÅ Tetap bersemangat !üí™
Let's meet again on the top of our own mountain!üòâ
